According to [[WorldCat]] the journal is alternately identified by ''Journal and ceramic abstracts'', ''Communications of the American Ceramic Society''. ''Journal of the American Ceramic Society''  superscedes ''Transactions of the American Ceramic Society'', and has absorbed ''Advanced Ceramic Materials''.<ref name=cassi> {{Cite web
